{"word":"ἀπομονόομαι","slug":"ἀπομονόομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπομονόομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μονόω'><el>μονόω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be excluded from</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be left alone</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}